title: H.EXE-Time of Contempt dark electro industrial EBM aggrotech
description:
Artist:    H.EXE
Album:     Time of Contempt
Label:     Halotan Records
More info: www.halotan.net

Time of Contempt is H.Exe's single promoting band's upcoming full-lenght album, Human Flesh Recipes.

The single consists of remixes by Sui Generis Umbra and Synchropatch of the title song, Time of Contempt and a couple of other songs that were published on compilations, but not on H.Exe's official releases.

Tracklist:
01. Time of Contempt
02. Time of Contempt (Sui Generis Umbra Remix)
03. Time of Contempt (Synchropath decomposition by Qbz)
04. The Garden is My Heart 
05. Just a Piece of Shit
06. Authorities (Riot!)
07. Astrophobos (v. 2011 feat. LaLuneNoire from Reactor7x)
